{"tid":742924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"根本職業就影響到一個人嘅性格，有d職業就係特別多仆街。","createTime":"2018-07-15T04:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T08:12:40.000Z","uid":71671,"like":13,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7888d38c8cd4a7f34b8d61c2c643169c68574668","tid":742924,"uid":71671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇留意，其他當然先天會影響性格，但係生活環境仲影響，會扭曲一個人原本嘅性格同態度，有d職業你會發覺好影令人變成仆街。<br />\n大家身邊有冇發現邊d?<br />\n<br />\n我先!<br />\n空姐<br />\n所有經紀行業<br />\n教師<br />\n社工<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論！"},{"pid":"2bd0bd9807fea73c675dd3794e3597caa34b58dc","tid":742924,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"係仆街先會做果d職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1dad0f68d3178d24ed314acbd623f64d5ac003b","tid":742924,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"經紀之餘 銀行前線都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a14498511a285e95aa2d4ef93e3406a7afe1e0","tid":742924,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1dad0f68d3178d24ed314acbd623f64d5ac003b","tid":742924,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"經紀之餘 銀行前線都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"會變成點呢？"},{"pid":"a7bb91c5aeb5eb60f296ac56dc969678ac7149c6","tid":742924,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:19:26.000Z","msg":"的士狗"},{"pid":"4bdcff283fc5235af8c06fda0ebc5b67faf12994","tid":742924,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a14498511a285e95aa2d4ef93e3406a7afe1e0","tid":742924,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1dad0f68d3178d24ed314acbd623f64d5ac003b","tid":742924,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"經紀之餘 銀行前線都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"會變成點呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"為左唔比老闆屌你唔到數<br />\n乜柒都要去做架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347b202faba71838df65d1538fd0adfb2ab72b1a","tid":742924,"uid":125920,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"係連登有邊份工未比人屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似得消防倖免"},{"pid":"c97ea503e970cf265dab44d732933576beebc04b","tid":742924,"uid":71671,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"逐個講下先<br />\n空姐算係比較冇咁極端，多數都係白鴒眼少少而已。會比較有種優越級，但係習慣湊鬼。不過生活因為燈紅酒綠，個人都比較貪慕虛榮少少。揀女朋友一定唔揀空姐！<br />\n<br />\n經紀就大家都知，他好像永遠對著你笑，笑得你心裡發寒。呢d人唔會好難相處，但好難做朋友，因為好假，好現實。識冇問題，唔好太熟就ok。<br />\n<br />\n教師就真係好多都仆街，好難相處。因為習慣左一入職就管幾十人（學生），平時好大枝野，覺得自己乜都岩哂！自己明明當年自己都唔係考得好好先做教師，就不停吹學歷有價。自己薪高糧準係因為自己努力讀書。<br />\n<br />\n社工唔洗講，冇乜社會功能又好高人工嘅寄生蟲，四圍掛個社福團體個名ｒ著數。"},{"pid":"73beae82b9364396828aa799e7515278ab74c47e","tid":742924,"uid":71671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"347b202faba71838df65d1538fd0adfb2ab72b1a","tid":742924,"uid":125920,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"係連登有邊份工未比人屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似得消防倖免"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"我自己因為平時對好多唔同人，真係睇得出好大分別"},{"pid":"68e3f41412b3e0eb31f252664ce3df7afa68c80c","tid":742924,"uid":71671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bdcff283fc5235af8c06fda0ebc5b67faf12994","